nodes.name: undecaprenyl-diphosphate phosphohydrolase
nodes.rxn: di-trans,poly-cis-Undecaprenyl diphosphate + H2O <=> di-trans,poly-cis-Undecaprenyl phosphate + Orthophosphate

nodes.name: UDP-N-acetylmuramoyl-L-alanine:D-glutamate ligase(ADP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + UDP-N-acetylmuramoyl-L-alanine + D-Glutamate <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + UDP-N-acetylmuramoyl-L-alanyl-D-glutamate

nodes.name: UDP-N-acetylmuramate:L-alanine ligase (ADP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + UDP-N-acetylmuramate + L-Alanine <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + UDP-N-acetylmuramoyl-L-alanine

nodes.name: (2E,6E)-farnesyl-diphosphate:isopentenyl-diphosphate cistransferase (adding 8 isopentenyl units)
nodes.rxn: trans,trans-Farnesyl diphosphate + 8 Isopentenyl diphosphate <=> di-trans,poly-cis-Undecaprenyl diphosphate + 8 Diphosphate
